PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774645561
OL,3,CConcerns after delayed hospital
OL,4,Ctransfer causes patient to miss
OL,5,Cappointment
OL,7,FA family has raised serious concerns
OL,8,Fabout patient safety after a man, who
OL,9,Fwas initially critically ill with
OL,10,Fsepsis, missed a vital hospital
OL,11,Fprocedure due to a delayed transfer
OL,12,Fbetween hospitals.
OL,14,FThey have told UTV they are worried
OL,15,Fthat the delay could now be putting
OL,16,Fhis health at risk as he is still
OL,17,Fwaiting for a new date for the
OL,18,Fprocedure.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774645561
OL,3,CConcerns after delayed hospital
OL,4,Ctransfer causes patient to miss
OL,5,Cappointment
OL,7,FKaren Gannon has been at her husband
OL,8,FMichael's bedside for 16 days. He
OL,9,Fbecame critically ill with sepsis,
OL,10,Fwhich his family believe may have been
OL,11,Flinked to his nephrostomy tube.
OL,13,FIt was inserted in November to treat a
OL,14,Fkidney stone.
OL,16,FAt one stage, the family was told he
OL,17,Fmight not survive but Michael, known
OL,18,Fas Harry to his family, pulled through.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774645561
OL,3,CConcerns after delayed hospital
OL,4,Ctransfer causes patient to miss
OL,5,Cappointment
OL,7,FNine days later, as his condition
OL,8,Fimproved, he was due to be transferred
OL,9,Ffrom Antrim Area Hospital to Belfast
OL,10,FCity Hospital to have the tube
OL,11,Freplaced.
OL,13,FHowever, the pre-booked private
OL,14,Fambulance was delayed by several
OL,15,Fhours, and he missed that vital
OL,16,Fprocedure.
OL,18,FMs Gannon said :"It didn't arrive
OL,19,Funtil 11:30 which was an hour and a
OL,20,Fhalf after the scheduled appointment.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774645561
OL,3,CConcerns after delayed hospital
OL,4,Ctransfer causes patient to miss
OL,5,Cappointment
OL,7,F"We went down to the city, arriving
OL,8,Fthere at about 12:05 to be told really
OL,9,Fjust basically to be waved away and
OL,10,Ftold that you'll have to take him back
OL,11,Fto Antrim.
OL,13,F"The clinic had finished and there was
OL,14,Fnobody there."
OL,16,FMr Gannon has since been transferred
OL,17,Fto the Royal Victoria Hospital where
OL,18,Fhe is still waiting for the tube to be
OL,19,Freplaced before being able to go home.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774645561
OL,3,CConcerns after delayed hospital
OL,4,Ctransfer causes patient to miss
OL,5,Cappointment
OL,7,FMrs Gannon said: "We're just waiting
OL,8,Fand waiting and that tube is still
OL,9,Fthere. I'm so aware that that hasn't
OL,10,Fbeen changed.
OL,12,F"Common sense would tell a reasonable
OL,13,Fperson that if that tube was
OL,14,Fcontaminated and caused sepsis, the
OL,15,Ffact that it's still in situ means
OL,16,Fthat it is just waiting to happen
OL,17,Fagain, and I would be very, very
OL,18,Ffoolish to think that it wouldn't."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774645561
OL,3,CConcerns after delayed hospital
OL,4,Ctransfer causes patient to miss
OL,5,Cappointment
OL,7,FIn a statement, the Northern Health
OL,8,Fand Social Care Trust said: "Due to
OL,9,Fsignificant pressures on available
OL,10,Ftransport for inpatient transfers that
OL,11,Fday, there was a delay in collecting
OL,12,FMr Gannon, and regrettably this
OL,13,Fresulted in him arriving in Belfast
OL,14,Flater than expected."
OL,16,FThey added: "We sincerely apologise to
OL,17,FMr Gannon and his family for the
OL,18,Fdistress caused by this experience.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774645561
OL,3,CConcerns after delayed hospital
OL,4,Ctransfer causes patient to miss
OL,5,Cappointment
OL,7,F"We are reviewing this alongside our
OL,8,Fcolleagues in Belfast Trust to
OL,9,Funderstand what could have been done
OL,10,Fdifferently...and to ensure that there
OL,11,Fare learnings for us in how inpatient
OL,12,Ftransfers are managed in future."
OL,14,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
